      "content": "i appreciate that, but it feels like a lot of empty words. people \"care,\" but they aren't the ones living in this body. they aren't the ones feeling the walls close in every single morning. it doesn't feel like i'm just going through a hard time, it feels like the end of the road has already been reached, and i'm just stuck in the traffic. what's the point of trying to find \"happiness\" when everything is just decaying? it feels like i've lost all my agency. i'm just a passenger in a life that isn't mine anymore.",
